11#ifndef API_AUDIO_CODECS_L16_AUDIO_ENCODER_L16_H_
12#define API_AUDIO_CODECS_L16_AUDIO_ENCODER_L16_H_
13
14#include <memory>
15#include <vector>
16
17#include "absl/types/optional.h"
18#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_codec_pair_id.h"
19#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_encoder.h"
20#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_format.h"
21#include "rtc_base/system/rtc_export.h"
22
23namespace webrtc {
24
25// L16 encoder API for use as a template parameter to
26// CreateAudioEncoderFactory<...>().
27struct RTC_EXPORT AudioEncoderL16 {
28 struct Config {
29 bool IsOk() const {
30 return (sample_rate_hz == 8000 || sample_rate_hz == 16000 ||
31 sample_rate_hz == 32000 || sample_rate_hz == 48000) &&
32 num_channels >= 1 && frame_size_ms > 0 && frame_size_ms <= 120 &&
33 frame_size_ms % 10 == 0;
34 }
35 int sample_rate_hz = 8000;
36 int num_channels = 1;
37 int frame_size_ms = 10;
38 };
39 static absl::optional<Config> SdpToConfig(const SdpAudioFormat& audio_format);
40 static void AppendSupportedEncoders(std::vector<AudioCodecSpec>* specs);
41 static AudioCodecInfo QueryAudioEncoder(const Config& config);
42 static std::unique_ptr<AudioEncoder> MakeAudioEncoder(
43 const Config& config,
44 int payload_type,
45 absl::optional<AudioCodecPairId> codec_pair_id = absl::nullopt);
46};
47
48} // namespace webrtc
49
50#endif // API_AUDIO_CODECS_L16_AUDIO_ENCODER_L16_H_
